data.description: Beautiful 3 Bed/1.75 Bath + Bonus Room Home In Continuously Developing NE Visalia! This gorgeous home has been recently has undergone a full rehab, with updates including new paint, windows, stove, granite countertops, flooring (carpet & laminate), new plumbing, eletrical and AC unit. You are greeted with the spacious living room, overlooking the front yard. Dining area just off the kitchen, and in the kitchen you will find granite counters, a new stove, and freshly painted cabinets. On one end of the home, you will find the two spare bedrooms, along with the full guest bathroom. On the opposite end of the home you have the designated laundry room and bonus room. In the master bedroom are dual closets and private slider access to the backyard. Master bath hosts dual sinks and a step in shower. The large backyard offers two citrus trees, a gated dog run, and plenty of room to entertain. This home is conveniently located near parks, schools, shopping centers, and dining, along with Riverway Sports Park and downtown Visalia!
